name: Cushing Middle School
directions:
On the main floor, go straight until you see the men's go around in the cafeteria and by the water fountains (two of them btw) turn around and there should be a door right there.

IF YOU ARE COMING FROM THE SIDE!
Go through the hall until you reach the patio that we have, turn and go down that long hall, turn to YOUR left and by the women's you should see a single door. Enter it and enjoy it there!
comment: I absolutely love that bathroom! As a non-binary person, I feel like that's the safest for me! Also, if you're a girl, you don't have to worry about being in the middle of others (if you do not like that) I suggest 1000/1000
